org.apache.poi.xwpf.usermodel

Enum BreakClear

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BreakClear>
      • org.apache.poi.xwpf.usermodel.BreakClear
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BreakClear> 

    public enum BreakClear
extends java.lang.Enum<BreakClear>
    Specifies the set of possible restart locations which may be used as to determine the next available line when a break's type attribute has a value of textWrapping.(指定一组可能的重新启动位置，当break的类型属性的值为textWrapping时，这些位置可用于确定下一个可用行。)
    Author:
    Gisella Bronzetti

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ALL
      Specifies that the text wrapping break shall advance the text to the next line in the WordprocessingML document which spans the full width of the line.(指定文本迂回符应将文本推进到WordcastingML文档中的下一行，该行跨越该行的整个宽度。)
      LEFT
      Specifies that the text wrapping break shall behave as follows: If this line is broken into multiple regions (a floating object in the center of the page has text wrapping on both sides: If this is the leftmost region of text flow on this line, advance the text to the next position on the line Otherwise, treat this as a text wrapping break of type all.(指定文本换行的行为如下：如果此行被分成多个区域（页面中心的浮动对象在两侧都有文本换行：如果这是该行上文本流的最左侧区域，则将文本前进到该行上的下一个位置否则，将其视为all类型的文本换行。)
      NONE
      Specifies that the text wrapping break shall advance the text to the next line in the WordprocessingML document, regardless of its position left to right or the presence of any floating objects which intersect with the line,(指定文本绕线应将文本推进到WordcastingML文档中的下一行，无论其从左到右的位置如何，也无论是否存在与该行相交的任何浮动对象，)
      RIGHT
      Specifies that the text wrapping break shall behave as follows: If this line is broken into multiple regions (a floating object in the center of the page has text wrapping on both sides: If this is the rightmost region of text flow on this line, advance the text to the next position on the next line Otherwise, treat this as a text wrapping break of type all.(指定文本绕转中断应如下行为：如果此行被分为多个区域（页面中心的浮动对象两侧都有文本绕转）：如果这是此行文本流的最右侧区域，请将文本前进到下一行的下一个位置否则，将其视为all类型的文本绕转中断。)

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • NONE

        public static final BreakClear NONE
        Specifies that the text wrapping break shall advance the text to the next line in the WordprocessingML document, regardless of its position left to right or the presence of any floating objects which intersect with the line,

        This is the setting for a typical line break in a document.

        (指定文本绕行符应将文本推进到WordcastingML文档中的下一行，无论其从左到右的位置如何，也无论是否存在与该行相交的任何浮动对象。这是文档中典型的行符的设置。)

      • LEFT

        public static final BreakClear LEFT
        Specifies that the text wrapping break shall behave as follows:
        • If this line is broken into multiple regions (a floating object in the center of the page has text wrapping on both sides:
          • If this is the leftmost region of text flow on this line, advance the text to the next position on the line
          • Otherwise, treat this as a text wrapping break of type all.
        • If this line is not broken into multiple regions, then treat this break as a text wrapping break of type none.
        (指定文本换行的行为如下：如果此行被分成多个区域（页面中心的浮动对象在两侧都有文本换行：如果这是该行上文本流的最左侧区域，则将文本前进到该行上的下一个位置否则，将其视为all类型的文本换行。如果此行未分为多个区域，则将此中断视为无类型的文本迂回中断。)
      • If the parent paragraph is right to left, then these behaviors are also reversed.

  • RIGHT

    public static final BreakClear RIGHT
    Specifies that the text wrapping break shall behave as follows:
    • If this line is broken into multiple regions (a floating object in the center of the page has text wrapping on both sides:
      • If this is the rightmost region of text flow on this line, advance the text to the next position on the next line
      • Otherwise, treat this as a text wrapping break of type all.
    • If this line is not broken into multiple regions, then treat this break as a text wrapping break of type none.
    • If the parent paragraph is right to left, then these beha viors are also reversed.

  • ALL

    public static final BreakClear ALL
    Specifies that the text wrapping break shall advance the text to the next line in the WordprocessingML document which spans the full width of the line.
